{"id":232880922,"title":"好文章分享 祝福你（妳）","content":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/ebc954e0-8cad-4850-ab53-62b7f52df0f3/full.jpeg\n\n◆婚姻的安身立命處　　　　\n⠀\n對於婚姻，我建議不要太理想化，因為理想和現實的落差會讓人失望。\n⠀\n像詩人徐志摩，他生性浪漫，追求理想，結果他的婚姻十分糟糕。\n⠀\n而學者胡適之，個性並不浪漫，雖然他的婚姻被視為過於傳統守舊，卻過得平穩安定，這是因為他以他的哲學思想做為安身立命之道。\n⠀\n人只要能找到安身立命處，人生就不會有問題。\n\n所謂的「安身立命 」，是要有獨立的人生理念，而不是把自己的生命，寄託在另外一個人身上。\n⠀\n夫妻是要共同生活一輩子的，同甘苦、共患難。\n\n並不僅僅我寫一首詩，你也寫一首詩；我畫畫，你也畫畫，這樣浪漫。\n\n當然，能夠做到夫唱婦隨，是非常好的，但最重要的是夫妻間能夠彼此諒解，彼此尊重，才能白頭偕老。\n—————————————————\n◇本文出處：《結婚好嗎?》\nhttps://www.ddc.com.tw/book/detail.php?id=1082\n⠀\n摘錄自【法鼓文化-心靈網路書店】","excerpt":"◆婚姻的安身立命處，⠀，對於婚姻，我建議不要太理想化，因為理想和現實的落差會讓人失望。⠀，像詩人徐志摩，他生性浪漫，追求理想，結果他的婚姻十分糟糕。⠀，而學者胡適之，個性並不浪漫，雖然他的婚姻被視為過","anonymousSchool":true,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"f11e8d02-6756-4376-9db3-e1cca4d2a66c","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-12T23:40:05.493Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-12T23:41:20.394Z","commentCount":2,"likeCount":2,"tags":[],"topics":["祝福大家永遠幸福"],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"結婚","forumAlias":"marriage","replyTitle":null,"gender":"M","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":2}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/ebc954e0-8cad-4850-ab53-62b7f52df0f3/full.jpeg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"cc68f3a1-d690-4609-aabb-df5d0b3b6f54","url":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/ebc954e0-8cad-4850-ab53-62b7f52df0f3/320.jpeg","normalizedUrl":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/ebc954e0-8cad-4850-ab53-62b7f52df0f3/320.jpeg","thumbnail":"https://megapx-assets.dcard.tw/images/ebc954e0-8cad-4850-ab53-62b7f52df0f3/320.jpeg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-12T23:40:05.493Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-12T23:41:20.394Z","width":320,"height":267},{"id":"cc68